<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Welcome to CHSS, <%= @user.first_name %> <%= @user.last_name %></h1>
    <p>
      You have successfully signed up as a <%= @user.role %> in CHSS,
      your username is: <%= @user.username %>.<br>
    </p>
    <p>
      To confirm your account, just follow <a href="<%= @url %>/<%= @user.id %>/activate">this</a> link.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for joining CHSS and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>